findings.title: Owner can pause/unpause contract
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to pause or unpause the contract at will.

findings.title: Owner can mint
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to mint without any restrictions.

findings.title: Owner Can Burn After _futureBurnDate
findings.description: The owner can burn tokens after _futureBurnDate, but _futureBurnDate does not get updated.
